# Welcome!

                                             -said no one ever :(

* Check me out on the [computercraft forums](http://www.computercraft.info/forums2/index.php?/user/15849-austinv11/)
* Check me out on [GitHub](https://github.com/austinv11/)

***

## Some of my (what I think are) cool projects:

* [![LootPlus Icon](http://dev.bukkit.org/media/images/72/465/LootPlus__2_.png)](http://dev.bukkit.org/bukkit-plugins/lootplus/) a Bukkit plugin

Man do I wish I was a web developer right now :/
